OL,3,CCash reward offered as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for arsonists who set fire
OL,5,Cto gym
OL,7,FITV Meridian's Kara Digby reports on
OL,8,Fthe fire at a Reading gym started by
OL,9,Farsonists.
OL,11,FA cash reward is being offered for
OL,12,Finformation to find the arsonists
OL,13,Fresponsible for a fire at a gym in
OL,14,FReading.
OL,16,FTwo people were seen on CCTV - forcing
OL,17,Ftheir way into Atrium Health Club in
OL,18,FJanuary - before pouring a flammable
OL,19,Fsubstance in the gym area - setting it
OL,20,Falight - and leaving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
