PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775999464
OL,3,CCash reward offered as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for arsonists who set fire
OL,5,Cto gym
OL,7,FThe damage was significant - and it
OL,8,Fmeant the business was closed for
OL,9,Fseveral weeks.
OL,11,FThe two people, who smashed their way
OL,12,Finto Atrium Health Club, didn't steal
OL,13,Fanything once inside.
OL,15,FWithin minutes they poured fuel over
OL,16,Fthe floor and set it alight - within
OL,17,Fseconds the building went up in flames.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
