PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775999464
OL,3,CCash reward offered as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for arsonists who set fire
OL,5,Cto gym
OL,7,FEmily Carey, who's from the health
OL,8,Fclub said it was a shock "Just to see
OL,9,Fthe reality of what had happened
OL,10,Fovernight. I mean, we'd all been here
OL,11,Fthe day before working, training and
OL,12,Fjust how quickly it all happened - It
OL,13,Fwas just so unexpected.
OL,15,FI think we were confused. We didn't
OL,16,Funderstand why it would have happened.
OL,17,FAnd yeah, just trying to puzzle it all
OL,18,Fout and, and think what we're going to
OL,19,Fdo after the impact that the fire had".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
