OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1775999464
OL,3,CCash reward offered as search
OL,4,Ccontinues for arsonists who set fire
OL,5,Cto gym
OL,7,FThe fire in January caused hundreds of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds worth of damage,
OL,9,Fforcing the business to close and shut
OL,10,Fclasses and programmes.
OL,12,FIt was thanks to the local community
OL,13,Fand regular gym goers the site could
OL,14,Fopen three weeks later.
OL,16,FTwo months on - and while Thames
OL,17,FValley Police continues to investigate
OL,18,Fthe attack - so far no arrests have
OL,19,Fbeen made.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
